I'll just do it the manual way.

3
00:00:06,689 --> 00:00:07,149
So hello.

4
00:00:08,070 --> 00:00:09,011
I'm Yuri Horniman.

5
00:00:10,031 --> 00:00:11,312
Everyone has slides with their names on it,

6
00:00:11,332 --> 00:00:12,193
but I have this.

7
00:00:12,513 --> 00:00:13,934
So I've been making games since 1991,

8
00:00:14,514 --> 00:00:17,556
and I've worn a lot of hats in that time.

9
00:00:17,596 --> 00:00:19,998
And today I'm here wearing my game designer hat.

10
00:00:20,558 --> 00:00:23,200
And so now I'd like to know a little bit more about you.

11
00:00:23,860 --> 00:00:25,902
Who here thinks of themselves primarily as a writer?

12
00:00:25,922 --> 00:00:30,185
OK, that's not as many as I expected.

13
00:00:31,245 --> 00:00:32,226
Wrote the whole thing for you writers.

14
00:00:33,494 --> 00:00:34,174
Narrative designer?

15
00:00:34,194 --> 00:00:37,175
Okay, that's a bunch, yeah, okay.

16
00:00:37,235 --> 00:00:37,716
Game designer?

17
00:00:37,736 --> 00:00:40,917
Okay, all right.

18
00:00:42,618 --> 00:00:44,799
